  "title": "In-house Security Officer",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></li><li><li><p>Conduct indoor and outdoor security patrols</p></li><li><p>Prevent unauthorized entry, trespass, intrusion and acts of vandalism</p></li><li><p>Prevent abuse of facilities provided in the Site by occupiers (including visitors)</p></li><li><p>Assist on worker check-in and check-out</p></li><li><p>Conduct audit check on security passes to ensure only authorized vehicle and personnel can access</p></li></li><li><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></li><li><li><p>Candidate <strong>must </strong>possess <strong>PLRD</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to write and read simple English.</p></li><li><p>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</p></li><li><p>Preferably Non-Executives specializing in Security/Armed Forces/Protective Services or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Alternate 6 days</p></li><li><p><strong>Singaporeans only</strong></p></li><p><p>Working location: <strong>Benoi </strong></p></p></li><li><br /><strong>Schedule</strong>:</li><li><li><p>Day shift / Night Shift</p></li></li></ul>",
